# Copy to .env.local and fill with your Supabase project (Dashboard → Settings → API).
# Local CLI defaults: http://127.0.0.1:54321 and the anon key printed by `supabase status`.
#
# Email/password login (/login): In Supabase Dashboard → Authentication → Providers,
# enable Email. For local dev, you can disable "Confirm email" under Auth → Email
# so sign-up can sign in immediately.
#
# If the browser shows "Failed to fetch" on sign-up/sign-in, the browser cannot reach
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL (check DevTools → Network). Use your cloud project URL
# (https://….supabase.co) unless Supabase is running on the same machine as the browser.

NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
